sets.title: Unstoppable lower body
sets.subTitle: Centr Power in Gym: Advanced week 10

workouts.title: Workout
workouts.introText:
From your quads to your calf muscles, these legs will not be stopped. Nail your form using the tutorials then bring the intensity.

For exercises that alternate sides, split the total number of specified reps between each side.

groups.title: Warm-up
groups.summary: Get your body ready for a strong workout.

groups.title: Round 1
groups.summary: Stick to the same weight and work those muscles to failure.

groups.title: Round 2
groups.summary: Split the total number of specified reps between each side.

groups.title: Round 3
groups.summary: Keep a steady tempo to build the burn in your glutes.

groups.title: Round 4
groups.summary: Pile up those reps for quad strength and definition.

groups.title: Round 5
groups.summary: Challenge your calf muscles to go out strong.
